name: numbing spoiled meat in insufferable warmth
description: Thrust your numbed flesh probes into a false flame to regain feeling. to purify the rot. to sterilize the cold. in something incapable of heat. let the blue light reanimate them with someone else’s life. let them burn. breath in the smoke. let your lungs cherish the suffocating need to consume. cry yourself to sleep. watch the flame die. wait for it to come back. die in its glow.
